{"claim_type": "measurement", "line_end": 699, "line_start": 699, "page_hint": null, "section": "Addendum to ORNL-TM-203", "text": "An addition has been made to the IBM-7090 program MURGATROYD to produce a rough graph of the reactor power versus time."}
{"claim_type": "measurement", "line_end": 699, "line_start": 699, "page_hint": null, "section": "Addendum to ORNL-TM-203", "text": "A logical tape 6 is required for storage of the power versus time results in addition to the standard input and output tapes."}
{"claim_type": "technical-statement", "line_end": 699, "line_start": 699, "page_hint": 18, "section": "Addendum to ORNL-TM-203", "text": "The plotting frequency (analogous to the printout frequency) is specified in columns 16-21 of the card containing the stop time and the number of ramp rate changes (see p 18, ORNL-TM-203)."}
{"claim_type": "measurement", "line_end": 699, "line_start": 699, "page_hint": null, "section": "Addendum to ORNL-TM-203", "text": "A sample of the graphical output is attached for the case given as an example on pages 19-25."}
{"claim_type": "measurement", "line_end": 699, "line_start": 699, "page_hint": null, "section": "Addendum to ORNL-TM-203", "text": "If the plotting frequency specified in the input is zero or blank, no plot is produced; however, a logical tape 6 must be specified even if no plot is desired."}
